<h1 id="typography">2. Bootstrap Typography practice</h1>
<div>
    <h2 style="background-color:lightblue">基本標題展示(搭配small tag)</h2>
    <h1>H1 tag 字體大小 36px<small>small tag</small></h1>
    <h2>H2 tag 字體大小 30px<small>small tag</small></h2>
    <h3>H3 tag 字體大小 24px<small>small tag</small></h3>
    <h4>H4 tag 字體大小 18px<small>small tag</small></h4>
    <h5>H5 tag 字體大小 14px<small>small tag</small></h5>
    <h6>H6 tag 字體大小 12px<small>small tag</small></h6>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<div style="background-color:lightblue"><h2>Bootstrap對字形(body部分)的預設格式</h2></div>
<ul>
    <li>預設字體大小為14px</li>
    <li>預設行寬(line-height)為1.48</li>
</ul>
<br />
<br />
<div style="background-color:lightblue"><h2>用p tag， 但希望可以凸顯文字 -使用.lead</h2></div>
<div>
    <p>原：</p>
    <p>我絕對不會說Bernice大大的生日在8月過後</p>
    <br />
    <p>加lead class</p>
    <p class="lead">我絕對不會說Bernice大大的生日在8月過後</p>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<div style="background-color:lightblue"><h2>常見的字型處理</h2></div>
<div>
    <p class="lead"><mark>Marked</mark> || <del>Deleted</del> || <s>Strikethrough</s> || <ins>Inserted</ins></p>
    <p class="lead"><u>Underlined</u> || <small>Small</small> || <strong>Blod</strong> || <em>Italics</em></p>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<div style="background-color:lightblue"><h2>文字對齊方式-使用.text-*</h2></div>
<div>
    <p class="text-left">Left aligned text.</p>
    <p class="text-center">Center aligned text.</p>
    <p class="text-right">Right aligned text.</p>
    <p class="text-justify">Justified text.</p>
    <p class="text-nowrap">No wrap text.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<div style="background-color:lightblue"><h2>Transformation class(需更新bootstrap版本)</h2></div>
<div>
    <p>原文：We create world-class mobile and web apps for enterprises, and help drive business success at leading organizations.</p>
    <p class="text-lowercase">We create world-class mobile and web apps for enterprises, and help drive business success at leading organizations.</p>
    <p class="text-uppercase">We create world-class mobile and web apps for enterprises, and help drive business success at leading organizations.</p>
    <p class="text-capitalize">We create world-class mobile and web apps for enterprises, and help drive business success at leading organizations.</p>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<div style="background-color:lightblue"><h2>縮寫(Abbreviations)</h2></div>
<div>
    <p>基本款：An abbreviation of the word attribute is <abbr title="attribute">attr</abbr>.</p>
    <p>小一點的font-size:<abbr title="HyperText Markup Language" class="initialism">HTML</abbr> is the best thing since sliced bread</p>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<div style="background-color:lightblue"><h2>地址<small>根據不同資訊使用不同的tag展現其風格，並在結尾加上br tag以保留格式</small></h2></div>
<div>
    <address>
        <strong>Twitter, Inc.</strong><br>
        795 Folsom Ave, Suite 600
        San Francisco, CA 94107
        <abbr title="Phone">P:</abbr> (123) 456-7890
    </address>
    <address>
        <strong>Full Name</strong><br>
        <a href="mailto:#">first.last@example.com</a>
    </address>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<div style="background-color:lightblue"><h2>預設引用(Blockquote options, 需更新bootstrap)</h2></div>
<div>
    <p><small>加入footer，將資料來源標籤用cite1包住</small></p>
    <blockquote>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer posuere erat a ante.</p>
        <footer>Someone famous in <cite title="Source Title">Source Title</cite></footer>
    </blockquote>
    <br />
    <blockquote class="blockquote-reverse">
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer posuere erat a ante.</p>
        <footer>Someone famous in <cite title="Source Title">Source Title</cite></footer>
    </blockquote>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<div style="background-color:lightblue"><h2>清單</h2></div>
<div>
    <p style="background-color:lightgray">無排序性</p>
    <ul>
        <li>第一項</li>
        <li>第二項</li>
        <li>第三項</li>
        <li>第四項
            <ul>               
                <li>4-1</li>
                <li>4-2</li>
                <li>4-3</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>第五項</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="background-color:lightgray">有排序性</p>
    <ol>
        <li>第一項</li>
        <li>第二項</li>
        <li>第三項</li>
        <li>
            第四項
            <ol>
                <li>4-1</li>
                <li>4-2</li>
                <li>4-3</li>
            </ol>
        </li>
        <li>第五項</li>
    </ol>
